6c6.title: Axiom of Choice: Guide
6c6.clickbait: Learn about the most controversial axiom of the 20th century.
6c6.text:
## Learning the Axiom of Choice ##

[multiple-choice(q_axiom_of_choice_history): This axiom has a rich and interesting history.  How much do you want to learn about? 
a: Give me all of the juicy history side-facts!
wants: [6c7] [6c9]
b: Eh, give me a short intro.
wants: [6c7]
-wants: [6c9]
c: Just stick to the mathematics, please.
-wants: [6c7] [6c9]
]

[multiple-choice(q_axiom_of_choice_mathematics): How heavy should the maths be that we show you? 
a: Lay it on me! Give me the formal logical notation.
wants: [6c8]
-wants: [6cb]
b: Just give me an intuitive description with words. No mathematical notation.
-wants: [6c8]
wants: [6cb]
]

%%box:
You will get the following pages:
%wants-requisite([6c7]):
Basic intro % 
%wants-requisite([6c9]):
History and controversy %
%wants-requisite([6c8]):
Definition (Formal) %
%wants-requisite([6cb]):
Definition (Intuitive) %
%%
